            <title>[LU-8612] Sync-on-Lock-Cancel locks should be handled per MDT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8612</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sync-on-Lock-Cancel locks are cross-MDT locks, now it&apos;s maintained in a global list, while it should be handled per target(MDT), otherwise it can&apos;t guarantee transaction commit before lock cancel.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
